{"tid":2207093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李宇軒家人公開信 冀國際關注12港青 「危險的路是自由唯一希望」","createTime":"2020-09-18T03:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T03:53:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa22af723397e6177079d39d63e071120f9202a","tid":2207093,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/P7YQTONM4FGPLNQKS7INDKGRKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FP7YQTONM4FGPLNQKS7INDKGRKA%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2e87abc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FP7YQTONM4FGPLNQKS7INDKGRKA%2F&h=793ec5da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/P7YQTONM4FGPLNQKS7INDKGRKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李宇軒家人公開信 冀國際關注12港青<br />\n「危險的路是自由唯一希望」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gUO3OgBXbFFKzRVmDhlBorhKr_Q=/1376x979/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ETOJXJZYVFBGJF6VYMRRH337BI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgUO3OgBXbFFKzRVmDhlBorhKr_Q%3D%2F1376x979%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FETOJXJZYVFBGJF6VYMRRH337BI.jpg&h=436befc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李宇軒<br />\n<br />\n【迎難而上】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陸委會反擊「窩藏罪犯」指控<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被內地指涉嫌偷越邊境而拘留的12名香港人，家屬至今仍未能知悉他們的情況，當中包括在港涉違反國安法被捕的「香港故事」成員李宇軒。李宇軒家人昨晚發公開信，希望國際社會敦促中國政府保證李安全、提供證據確認其實際位置、以及讓他和家人委託律師接觸。其家人直言，李竭盡全力為香港爭取民主，呼籲國際社會與李宇軒站在一起，保障他的基本人權。<br />\n<br />\n李宇軒家人昨日先後在fb、Twitter及Instagram以「Andy Is Missing」分別開設專頁或頻道，希望令香港大眾及國際社會，繼續關注及聲援12位現時被中國拘留且未獲得法律支援港人的嚴峻情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求保障拘留期間人權<br />\n<br />\n專頁昨晚刊出聲稱是其家人發出的聲明，呼籲國際社會與李宇軒站在一起，在他被拘留期間，維護其基本人權，並向中國當局提出三項要求，包括確保李宇軒安全、提供證據確認他的實際位置，同時容許他接觸受家人委託的律師。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又披露更多關於李宇軒的背景，家人形容李是一名年輕的傑出程式員，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其家人又指，李一直相信香港法冶，他決定不在港接受審訊，反映他對香港法律制度信心完全崩潰，形容12人選擇最危險的道。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《大公報》昨日引述消息人士，指被拘留12人健康狀況良好，聲稱已依法行使委託律。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n協助家屬的抗爭派鄒家成指，不清楚其他被拘留者是否同被當局委派律師，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而14名中西區民主派區議員昨向特首林鄭月娥發公開信，指被拘留港人家屬遵從中。。。。。"},{"pid":"f4dada3f8846dadad8096adea24d204382cd45f0","tid":2207093,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"2佰萬人唔見咗。"},{"pid":"2026ba74868596f36326b68793bb05db536045a4","tid":2207093,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c429161ed71270b36bda0999c6ba3ff5d08ea6","tid":2207093,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AndyIsMissing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAndyIsMissing%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=5ed631ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AndyIsMissing/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/andy_is_missing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fandy_is_missing&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=ac787116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/andy_is_missing</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/andy_is_missing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fandy_is_missing&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=77f75dcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/andy_is_missing</a>"},{"pid":"175eb63b4225159c409f5a31fb35864e1cfe10f8","tid":2207093,"uid":147308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63e0e5116058e9fa24dc2e79e29194404ccab5dc","tid":2207093,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacc1dbb55930099816db7842e2727596e04dbe7","tid":2207093,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}